summary: Kaettekita Mario Bros., an enhanced port of Mario Bros. for the Japanese-only Famicom Disk System, contains several scenes and...
caption:
Kaettekita Mario Bros., an enhanced port of Mario Bros. for the Japanese-only Famicom Disk System, contains several scenes and features not present in any other versions of the game. One of these is a roulette screen after getting a Game Over, where extra lives can be won depending on how many Marios appear in the slots. The screen features a unique jumping sprite for Mario, where he raises his hands up in joy as he jumps offscreen.
Main Blog | Twitter | Patreon | Store | Small Findings | Source

title: Gokú en versión Dragon Ball GT llegará a Dragon Ball FighterZ
body:
Gokú de Dragon Ball GT se unirá a Dragon Ball FighterZ como un personaje jugable a través de contenido descargable pagado, revela el último número mensual V-Jump. El movimiento especial de GT de Gokú es “Super Kamehameha”, que lo transforma en Super Saiyan 3 cuando quedan dos o menos miembros del equipo. Sus ataques especiales […]

summary: Brad Sams: Now Hearing Sources Say Xbox Game Pass Isn't Coming To Nintendo Switch, At Least Near Term
title: Brad Sams: Now Hearing Sources Say Xbox Game Pass Isn't Coming To Nintendo Switch, At Least Near Term
body:
Brad Sams: Now Hearing Sources Say Xbox Game Pass Isn’t Coming To Nintendo Switch, At Least Near Term

Brad Sams, who is one of the writers for Windows Central, has now heard from multiple close sources that Xbox Games Pass via x-Cloud streaming isn’t destined for the Nintendo Switch. It could come in the future, but right now it doesn’t seem to be something that’s happening, which is a shame. However, it still seems as though Xbox One title Ori and the Blind Forestcould still come to Nintendo…

View On WordPress

summary: I want the ability to open a shop up in animal crossing where villagers in your town (and even those that don't) will visit and...
body: I want the ability to open a shop up in animal crossing where villagers in your town (and even those that don’t) will visit and buy from your shop. Every once in a while you’ll get a character like isabelle or one of the holiday characters.
